title: Spider-Man J - Digest v1 Japanese Knights (2008|Digital|APG-E)
description:
Spider-Man, manga style? Yes! This formerly Japan-only comic is by Marc Sumerak (Adapter), Zeb Wells (Adapter), Yamanaka Akira (Author, Illustrator), Yuko Fukami (Translator), and features some fun and zany adventures of our favorite wall-crawler. Promotional info from the collected edition - "Fresh from Japan...Spider-Man J! Originally published only in that country, Spider-Man J enjoyed a large following of loyal readers. Now, fans here can enjoy Spider-Man J's manga-styled adventures, collected for the first time in America and translated in English for your reading pleasure! Reprinting stories from Spider-Man Family #1-6."


This digital copy is by AnPymGold-Empire. Thanks to them for their efforts; please seed, and enjoy! :-)
